<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Create your free Linkly account.">
    <title>Create an account — Linkly</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #101828;
            --ink: #344054;
            --muted: #667085;
            --line: #e4e7ec;
            --brand: #6941c6;
            --brand-dark: #53389e;
            --brand-soft: #f4f3ff;
            --cyan: #12b7c4;
            --success: #067647;
            --success-soft: #ecfdf3;
            --danger: #b42318;
            --danger-soft: #fef3f2;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--navy);
            background: #ffffff;
            font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        button, input { font: inherit; }

        .page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(520px, 1.08fr) minmax(430px, 0.92fr);
        }

        .form-panel {
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 44px 28px;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 5% 5%, rgba(18, 183, 196, 0.07), transparent 22%),
                #ffffff;
        }

        .form-shell {
            width: min(460px, 100%);
        }

        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 11px;
            margin-bottom: 44px;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-size: 21px;
            font-weight: 850;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .brand-mark {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--cyan));
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(105, 65, 198, 0.23);
        }

        .brand-mark svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }

        .welcome {
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .welcome h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 38px;
            line-height: 1.08;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
        }

        .welcome p {
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .notice {
            margin-bottom: 19px;
            border: 1px solid #fecdca;
            border-radius: 11px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            color: var(--danger);
            background: var(--danger-soft);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 650;
            line-height: 1.45;
        }

        .signup-form {
            display: grid;
            gap: 17px;
        }

        .field {
            display: grid;
            gap: 7px;
        }

        .field-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .field label {
            color: var(--ink);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 750;
        }

        .field-hint {
            color: #98a2b3;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .input-wrap {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-icon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 15px;
            width: 19px;
            height: 19px;
            color: #98a2b3;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .field input {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 52px;
            border: 1px solid #d0d5dd;
            border-radius: 11px;
            padding: 0 46px;
            color: var(--navy);
            background: #ffffff;
            outline: none;
            transition: border 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease;
        }

        .field input:focus {
            border-color: var(--brand);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(105, 65, 198, 0.11);
        }

        .password-toggle {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            right: 11px;
            border: 0;
            padding: 7px;
            color: var(--muted);
            background: transparent;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 750;
            cursor: pointer;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .password-rules {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 7px 12px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .rule {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            color: #98a2b3;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .rule::before {
            content: "✓";
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: var(--success);
            background: var(--success-soft);
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .submit-button {
            min-height: 52px;
            margin-top: 3px;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 11px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--brand), #7f56d9);
            font-weight: 800;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(105, 65, 198, 0.24);
            transition: transform 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease;
        }

        .submit-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(105, 65, 198, 0.31);
        }

        .login-link {
            margin: 24px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .login-link a {
            color: var(--brand);
            font-weight: 750;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .visual-panel {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px clamp(42px, 6vw, 82px);
            color: #ffffff;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 15%, rgba(18, 183, 196, 0.34), transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 88%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent 24%),
                linear-gradient(145deg, #292056, #53389e 54%, #087f8c 125%);
        }

        .visual-panel::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 390px;
            height: 390px;
            right: -230px;
            bottom: -150px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 55px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035), 0 0 0 110px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        }

        .visual-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 530px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 7px 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 750;
        }

        .eyebrow span {
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #5fe7d8;
        }

        .visual-content h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 66px);
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        .visual-content > p {
            margin: 23px 0 35px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .benefits {
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .benefit {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 13px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.87);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 650;
        }

        .benefit-icon {
            width: 29px;
            height: 29px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 9px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .quote-card {
            margin-top: 42px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.17);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.65;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .quote-card strong {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 920px) {
            .page { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .visual-panel { display: none; }
            .form-panel { min-height: 100vh; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .form-panel {
                align-items: start;
                padding: 28px 20px;
            }

            .brand { margin-bottom: 35px; }
            .welcome h1 { font-size: 32px; }
            .password-rules { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="page">
        <section class="form-panel">
            <div class="form-shell">
                <a class="brand" href="/login">
                    <span class="brand-mark">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/>
                            <path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    Linkly
                </a>

                <header class="welcome">
                    <h1>Create your account</h1>
                    <p>Start creating cleaner links and tracking every visit. It only takes a minute.</p>
                </header>

                <% if (locals.error) { %>
                    <div class="notice"><%= error %></div>
                <% } %>

                <form class="signup-form" action="/user" method="POST">
                    <div class="field">
                        <label for="name">Full name</label>
                        <div class="input-wrap">
                            <svg class="input-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/>
                                <path d="M4 21a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/>
                            </svg>
                            <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name" value="<%= locals.formData ? formData.name : "" %>" required autofocus>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="field">
                        <label for="email">Email address</label>
                        <div class="input-wrap">
                            <svg class="input-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/>
                                <path d="m4 6 8 6 8-6"/>
                            </svg>
                            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="you@example.com" autocomplete="email" value="<%= locals.formData ? formData.email : "" %>" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="field">
                        <div class="field-row">
                            <label for="password">Password</label>
                            <span class="field-hint">Minimum 8 characters</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-wrap">
                            <svg class="input-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <rect x="4" y="10" width="16" height="11" rx="2"/>
                                <path d="M8 10V7a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"/>
                            </svg>
                            <input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Create a strong password" autocomplete="new-password" minlength="8" pattern="(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*\d)(?=.*[^A-Za-z0-9]).{8,}" title="Use at least 8 characters with uppercase, lowercase, number, and symbol." required>
                            <button class="password-toggle" type="button" onclick="togglePassword(this)">Show</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="password-rules" aria-label="Password requirements">
                            <span class="rule">Uppercase letter</span>
                            <span class="rule">Lowercase letter</span>
                            <span class="rule">Number</span>
                            <span class="rule">Symbol</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button class="submit-button" type="submit">Create free account →</button>
                </form>

                <p class="login-link">Already have an account? <a href="/login">Sign in</a></p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <aside class="visual-panel">
            <div class="visual-content">
                <div class="eyebrow"><span></span>Free to get started</div>
                <h2>Your links deserve a better home.</h2>
                <p>Join Linkly and turn every long URL into a clean, trackable link built for better sharing.</p>

                <div class="benefits">
                    <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon">✓</span>Unlimited short links</div>
                    <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon">↗</span>Live click tracking</div>
                    <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon">⌁</span>One organized dashboard</div>
                </div>

                <div class="quote-card">
                    “Clean links make every campaign look more intentional—and knowing what people click makes the next one better.”
                    <strong>The Linkly promise</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </main>

    <script>
        function togglePassword(button) {
            const input = document.getElementById("password");
            const showing = input.type === "text";
            input.type = showing ? "password" : "text";
            button.textContent = showing ? "Show" : "Hide";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
